# River generator
This is a basic MarkovJunior example that procedurally generates rivers.

Load the library first:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
PacletDirectoryLoad[
  NotebookDirectory[]//ParentDirectory
];
Needs["CoffeeLiqueur`Workshop`MarkovJunior`"->"mj`"];

