%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
Create a set of rules following this pattern:

```
{
  All | 1,  (* apply the rule to all found matches or to 1 randomly chosen match *)
  _Integer | Infinity, (* maximum number of steps for this rule set *)
                       (* allowed symmetry operations *)
  Automatic | All | None | "Mirror" | ...,
  {
    a -> b,  (* rule 1 *)
    c -> d   (* rule 2 *)
    ...
  }
}
```

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Create a set of rules following this pattern:

```
{
  All | 1,  (* apply the rule to all found matches or to 1 randomly chosen match *)
  _Integer | Infinity, (* maximum number of steps for this rule set *)
                       (* allowed symmetry operations *)
  Automatic | All | None | "Mirror" | ...,
  {
    a -> b,  (* rule 1 *)
    c -> d   (* rule 2 *)
    ...
  }
}
```

